  <thing id="fBlaDauPre" name="Dauntless Presence" description="Few would accuse you of sentimentaIity toward yourcompanions, yet you hate to see them harmed. When they flag, your cause is weakened. That cannot be allowed. When your allies pause to heal, your fanaticism to continue the fight is bolstered.\n\n{b}Benefit:{/b} When an ally spends a healing surge while adjacent to you, you gain temporary hit points equal to your Charisma modifier." compset="ClassFeat">
